        "chatId": "1849095413",
        "message": "=🎨 AI Social Media Content Review\n\nYour new social media post has been generated successfully.\n\nPlease review the generated post and image, then choose one of the following options:\n\n1️⃣ Publish\nPublish the post to Facebook.\n\n2️⃣ Regenerate\nGenerate a new version of the post and image.\n\n3️⃣ Cancel\nDiscard this post without publishing.\n\n⚠️ Please reply with 1, 2, or 3 only.",
